According to the Ministry of Health, Labour and Welfare, a number of facilities were confirmed, such as raising the usage fee only for three-year-olds or older who were eligible for assistance, and raising the price in October.
There were also complaints about the free call center established by the Cabinet Office.
The Ministry of Health said, "There is no reason to raise prices."
