[Saga Torrential Rainfall and Support Wheel] Specialty Noodles "Taromen" Perform at evacuation shelter Management Co-op, cheering victims|Saga Shimbun News|Saga Shimbun
Children who enjoy "Taromen" the soul food of Omachi on the way home from the bath = Migo, Omachi Town General Welfare Center
"Omachi Taromen Steering Council" (Representative of Kensuke Suzuyama) made at a restaurant offering taromen, a specialty of Omachi-cho, performed taromen at Misato, Machi General Welfare Center, which is a shelter for people affected by heavy rain on the night of 25th.
