Members calling for drivers to drive safely = Saga Nakatakamae in Tojo, Karatsu City
To coincide with the "Autumn Traffic Safety Prefectural People's Movement," the Karatsu Tobacco Sales Cooperative held street activities on the 26th on the street of Saga Nakataka, Waseda in Tojo, Karatsu City.
