The reason why YouTuber, a super personality, became a regular employee.
Ask the president who hired (bizSPA!
9/27 (Fri) 8:47
YouTuber is now very popular with young people.
Although it is not uncommon for companies to use it to advertise their products, some companies have started a unique system called "YouTuber Adoption" that they employ as regular employees.
Direct Marketing Mix Co., Ltd. (DmMiX) is a major business of corporate CRM (customer relationship management).
What does it mean to adopt YouTuber?
I listened to Mr. Yuki Kobayashi, Representative Director of DmMiX and Representative Director of Staff First, a subsidiary that actually adopted YouTuber.
i want to support young people who work hard with youtuber.
What is YouTuber adoption in the first place?
Yuki Kobayashi (hereinafter, Kobayashi): Now, YouTuber is a profession that many young people have longed for.
It is also ranked in the career rankings that elementary school students want to get in the future, and the number of young people aiming for will increase steadily in the future.
Until now, we have adopted and supported young people chasing dreams such as bandmen and comedians.
In the same way, it is "YouTuberr Adoption" to support young people who are chasing their dream of becoming YouTuber.
There is an image that YouTuber is something that individuals voluntarily post videos, but why did you decide to adopt YouTuber?
Kobayashi: While many young people yearn for the profession of YouTuber, there is a reality that most YouTuber can't get the revenue that they thought.
There are many creators who make and post videos while working part-time, and those who do not allow their family to recognize the existence of YouTuber.
In this initiative, we will provide an environment for salary and content creation to the creators we hired.
At first, we will support the demerits of the profession called YouTuber, which will inevitably become unstable.
