On the 27th, "Okayama Sunny Country Bicchu Marche" (hosted by the prefectural Bicchu Prefectural Bureau, etc.) to promote sightseeing spots and specialty products in the Bicchu area started on a two-day schedule in the plaza of JR Osaka Station.
