On the 28th, Kigenji Makunouchi, the twin brother of Juryo Takanofuji, who was urged to retire voluntarily by the Japan Sumo Association for assaulting sumo wrestlers at the Grand Sumo Tournament, said, "I accept it firmly and start from negative rather than zero from the next place."
He was interviewed at Ryogoku Kokugikan in Tokyo, where he participated in Hanazumo.
